{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action/task-1","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 1","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U sledećoj vežbi, ćete čuti pitanja o ličnim podacima.</p>\n<p>Vaš cilj je slušati, razumeti koje informacije su potrebne, zatim pogledati obrazac ili pronaći tačan odgovor.</p>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio. Identifikujte kakve informacije su potrebne. Zatim, koristite obrazac ispod da popunite rečenicu sa tačnim odgovorom.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Campo del formulario</span></th>\n<th align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Entrada del formulario</span></th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Nombre</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Luna</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Primer apellido</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Méndez</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Segundo apellido</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Pérez</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Nacionalidad</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">chilena</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Profesión</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">científica de datos</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Correo electrónico</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">luna.mendez@andes.com</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Número de teléfono</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">+56 923 881 240</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Edad</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\"><span class=\"highlighted-text\">25</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nombre?</span> se može koristiti za pitala ime osobe. Kada pogledaš deo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">nombre</span>, videćeš da je njihovo ime <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Luna</span>. Stoga, kompletan odgovor će biti <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mi nombre es Luna</span>.</p>\n<p>U španskom, mnogo pitanja počinje sa rečima kao što su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cuál</span> (ko), <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Cómo</span> (kako), <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Quieres</span> (da li želiš), i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puedes</span> (da li možeš).</p>\n<p>Ova pitanja pomažu u stvaranju uobičajenih i poštovanih fraza, kao što su:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cuál es tu nombre?</span> - Kako se zoveš?</li>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo te llamas?</span> - Kako se zoveš?</li>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Quieres que te ayude?</span> - Da li želiš da ti pomognem?</li>\n<li><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes repetirlo?</span> - Možeš li ponoviti?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Često ćete videti da španski ignoriše lične zamenice <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span> (ti). Primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo te llamas?</span> umesto <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo tú te llamas?</span>.</p>\n<p>Ovo je zato što španski glagoli već pokazuju ličnu zamenicu u svojim konjugacijama, čineći rečenicu jasnom i prirodnom bez potrebe da se kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span>.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action/task-1"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Mi nombre es BLANK</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"Luna","feedback":"<p>Pokušaj da pronađeš deo koji je povezan sa imenom.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room1.png","characters":[{"character":"Esteban","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_personal_details_just_questions.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0.75,"finishTimestamp":2.15},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1.4,"finishTime":2.4,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Cuál es tu nombre?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Esteban","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.5,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action","dashedName":"task-1","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-basic-personal-details","module":"es-a1-module-sharing-your-personal-details","block":"es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action","isFirstStep":true,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-action/task-2","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-28","id":"695d59703e704936dced2be9","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-personal-details-in-a